They secure a peach-hued recycled cotton upper, fortified with tonal synthetic leather at the toe and heel. Time4Change branding adorns a midfoot overlay constructed from recycled polyurethane.

results.name: Ralph Sampson Low Infant 'Time4Change - Peacoat'
results.story: The PUMA Ralph Sampson Low Infant ‘Peacoat’ is taken from the brand’s ‘Time4Change’ collection, an eco-friendly assortment of apparel and footwear built with sustainable materials. This mini version of the retro hoops shoe features dual hook-and-loops straps and a navy textile upper constructed from recycled cotton. The sneaker’s uniform palette is enlivened by a striped detailing on the collar lining and Ralph Sampson’s gold-foil signature on the lateral quarter panel. Time4Change branding adorns an accompanying midfoot overlay.

results.name: Cruise Rider Infant 'Viridian Green'
results.story: The PUMA Cruise Rider Infant ‘Viridian Green’ combines exaggerated tooling with a layered, retro-inspired build. Emerald mesh on the upper is fortified with overlays in textile and synthetic suede, as well as a hint of patent leather wrapped around the heel. The sneaker is mounted on a stacked injection-molded EVA midsole, good for lightweight cushioning with each step. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a waffle-style tread for reliable traction.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Black White'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant ‘Black White’ delivers a scaled-down version of the classic silhouette, featuring a lightly refreshed build made for the 21st century. The upper is constructed from the sneaker’s eponymous material, unheard of for use in a basketball shoe in 1968 — the year the low-top originally released. In addition to an off-white suede Formstrip, contrast-hued branding elements include an archival tongue tag and a gold-foil PUMA Suede wordmark on the lateral side panel.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'High Risk Red'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant ‘High Risk Red’ brings back the 1968 basketball shoe in a lightly redesigned iteration made for little feet. The upper is immersed in an eye-catching shade of crimson, contrasted by an off-white suede Formstrip and metallic gold PUMA Suede branding. A removable foam sockliner combines with a textile-lined interior to deliver a comfortable fit. Underfoot, a non-marking rubber outsole provides durable traction.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Black'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant ‘Black’ retrieves a vintage basketball shoe from the brand’s late ‘60s archive, scaled down and dipped in ebony for little feet. The one-note finish on the suede upper is disrupted by the sneaker’s branding hits, including a woven tongue tag and ‘PUMA Suede’ stamped in gold lettering on the lateral side panel. The sneaker is mounted on a matching black rubber cupsole, featuring textured sidewalls and a grid-like traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Pink Lady'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant ‘Pink Lady’ features a pastel finish throughout the sneaker’s eponymous upper. The subtle pink hue is contrasted by an off-white suede Formstrip and a PUMA Suede callout in metallic gold lettering. Soft textile lines the interior, which pairs with a removable foam sockliner to provide a comfortable fit for growing feet. The rubber cupsole is undergirded with a traction pattern originally developed for the hardwood.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Peacoat'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant ‘Peacoat’ features a classic two-tone palette on a scaled down edition of the vintage hoops shoe originally released in 1968. Lightly refreshed for the 21st century, the low-top makes use of a navy suede upper with a contrasting off-white Formstrip. A PUMA Suede wordmark in gold foil lettering shines on the lateral quarter panel. Soft textile lines the interior, while a removable Kinder-Fit sockliner provides step-in comfort.

Additional abrasion-resistant overlays bolster the toe and heel. No-tie elastic laces and a hook-and-loop strap combine with dual webbing pull tabs for easy on and off. Underfoot, left and right labeled rubber outsoles feature forefoot flex grooves that promote the natural motion of the foot.

Versa Pump Fury 'Black'
results.story: Reebok's Versa Pump Fury follows the formula of the iconic running sneaker with kid-specific modifications. Introduced in July 2019, this all-black edition flaunts a mesh upper with deconstructed synthetic overlays, a protective toe guard and two pull tabs. Young wearers can squeeze the tech-inspired tongue pump for a squeaking sound. A cushioned midsole and full-length rubber outsole simulate the platform of the original adult model.

results.name: Versa Pump Fury 'Black'
results.story: Based on the Steven Smith-designed runner, the Reebok Versa Pump Fury simulates its unconventional look with kid-specific updates. This iteration—from July 2019—works a grey mesh and synthetic leather upper with tonal tabs and a hook-and-loop strap for easy, pull-on entry. The tongue apparatus emits a squeaking noise when pressed. Supporting growing feet, the sneaker has a cushioned midsole and two-tone rubber outsole.

results.name: Versa Pump Fury 'Berry'
results.story: The Reebok Versa Pump Fury readapts distinctive DNA from the iconic 90s running sneaker to help little ones build mobility. Launched in June 2019, this edition helps keep the foot cool and dry in Berry mesh reinforced with dual-colored leather. The tech-inspired pump on the tongue releases a squeak when pressed. A foam midsole and rubber outsole provide cushioned protection for stability and abrasion resistance.

results.name: Versa Pump Fury TD 'Royal'
results.story: The Reebok Versa Pump Fury TD translates the iconic elements of the 90s basketball shoe for small feet. Introduced in June 2019, this 'Royal' kids' iteration is constructed with a synthetic leather and textile upper in a tricolor palette and a hook-and-loop closure for easy on and off. Featuring a classic logo, the foam midsole and rubber outsole support first steps.

results.name: Versa Pump Fury SYN TD 'Blue Green Pink'
results.story: The Reebok Versa Pump Fury SYN TD 'Blue Green Pink' proves that little feet require stability too. Modeled after the adult version, the kids' sneaker is equipped with a synthetic leather and textile upper and exhibits a slip-on design for fuss-free wear. The pump on the tongue gives out a 'squeak' when pressed to entertain old and young. At the back, a hook-and-loop strap adjusts to meet the demands of growing feet while a pink and blue outsole below keeps traction for little steps.

results.name: Versa Pump Fury SYN GP 'Luster Pink'
results.story: The Reebok Versa Pump Fury SYN GP readapts the iconic design of the Pump Fury to assist toddlers in building mobility. Unveiled in October 2018, this version supports the foot in breathable mesh structured by Luster Pink synthetic leather with a hook-and-loop strap and squeaking tongue pump. Reflective accents are layered under the toe guard. A cushioned midsole and durable rubber outsole complete the sneaker.

results.name: VentureFlex Chase 2 'Coal'
results.story: Reebok's VentureFlex Chase 2 delivers comfort and support for toddlers. Updated in August 2018, this Coal iteration is illustrated with a snake eye, fangs and serpentine scale graphic on the textile upper and synthetic leather hook-and-loop fastener. Tongue and heel branding and a Vector logo printed on the lateral nod to sport heritage. The sneaker's cushioned midsole is set atop a rubber outsole with molded smileys.

Assert 8 TD 'Halo Grey Cerise'
results.story: Built for toddlers, the Under Armour Assert 8 TD ‘Halo Grey Cerise’ features a ventilated grey mesh upper reinforced with tonal synthetic overlays at the toe and heel. No-tie stretch bungee laces combine with an adjustable hook and loop strap to deliver easy on and off. The convenient slip-on silhouette rides on a soft midsole made with Under Armour’s Charged Cushioning, good for impact absorption and a smooth ride.

results.name: Thrill TD 'Red'
results.story: Designed for flexibility and cushioning, the Under Armour Thrill TD 'Red' sneaker is engineered for supportive movement. A scaled-down version of the adult-sized silhouette, the shoe features a ventilated mesh upper and anti-odor footbed to help keep small feet cool and fresh. Responsive, lightweight foam and a flex-grooved outsole deliver comfortable, natural strides.

The upper, crafted from orange velvet, is designed to mimic the appearance of the three-eyed fish that populate Springfield’s lakes, a mutant species created as a byproduct of the city’s nuclear power plant. Elastic side accents work alongside hook-and-loop closures for a snug, secure fit. Underfoot, a gum rubber waffle outsole provides grippy traction.

results.name: The Simpsons x Slip-On V TD 'Maggie'
results.story: Made for toddlers, The Simpsons x Vans Slip-On V TD ‘Maggie’ is drawn from a larger collection made in partnership with the long-running animated series. This pair celebrates the youngest Simpson child, featuring a pastel canvas upper covered in an all-over graphic print made up of Maggie’s likeness. A pull tab at the heel works in tandem with hook and loop closure to provide easy on and off, while a gum rubber waffle outsole delivers grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: The Simpsons x Old Skool V TD 'El Barto'
results.story: Made for toddlers, The Simpsons x Vans Old Skool V TD ‘El Barto’ is taken from an expansive collection developed in partnership with the iconic animated series. The low-top silhouette, secured with dual hook-and-loop straps, features an upper that combines black suede with contrasting red canvas. The latter material is utilized on side panels that mimic brick walls, defaced with graffiti perpetrated by Bart’s vandalizing alter-ego.

results.name: The Simpsons x Sk8-Hi Zip TD 'Simpsons Family 1987-2020'
results.story: Made for toddlers, The Simpsons x Vans Sk8-Hi Zip TD ‘Simpsons Family 1987-2020’ is taken from a larger collection celebrating the long-running TV series. The high-top features different family portraits on each sneaker’s canvas side panels, one depicting the Simpsons in the year of their creation, the other displaying what the characters look like now. The rest of the upper utilizes black suede on the vamp and heel, the latter equipped with zip closure for easy on and off.

results.name: The Simpsons x Sk8-Hi Zip TD 'Lisa 4 Prez'
results.story: Made for toddlers, The Simpsons x Vans Sk8-Hi Zip TD ‘Lisa 4 Prez’ is taken from an expansive collection dedicated to the long-running animated series. The high-top features a pastel lavender finish on an upper built with canvas and suede. The lateral side panel is embellished with a ‘Lisa Simpson for President’ patch, with the slogan repeated in yellow lettering across the white rubber midsole. A pull tab at the tongue combines with zippered closure along the heel for easy on and off.

The diminutive silhouette mimics Mickey’s ensemble, highlighted by a black, red and yellow color scheme, and the character’s white gloves on both straps of the shoe’s closure system.

results.name: Disney x Old Skool Velcro Toddler '80s Mickey'

results.story: Vans released a range of footwear and apparel inspired by Marvel superheroes in June 2018. The Marvel x Authentic Toddler 'Marvel Heads' features an Off-White canvas upper dotted with the heads of some of Marvel’s Avengers superheroes. The toddler-size sneaker also has white laces, a waffle outsole, a white midsole and Vans and Marvel co-branding on the insoles.

results.name: Marvel x Slip-On Toddler 'Hulk'
results.story: HULK SMASH! The Marvel x Slip-On Toddler 'Hulk' is a toddler-sized Slip-On featuring a graphic of the Hulk’s green foot ripping through a black-and-white checkerboard print. The low-profile canvas upper sits above a white rubber midsole and waffle outsole, while Marvel and Vans co-branding mark the insole.

results.name: Marvel x SK8-Hi Zip Toddler 'Spiderman'
results.story: Your friendly neighborhood Spider-Man swings onto the Marvel x SK8-Hi Zip Toddler 'Spiderman' with a toddler-sized SK8-Hi. Featuring a red and blue canvas upper, an embossed web pattern can be seen over the red panelling and white Sidestripe and zipper entry at the heel. A graphic of Spiderman's head hangs from lateral side collar, while another peers up from the medial side midsole. A zipper on the heel allows for easier foot entry for toddlers.

results.name: Sk8-Hi Zip LX Toddler 'Spongebob Checkerboard'
results.story: The Vans Sk8-Hi Zip LX Toddler 'SpongeBob Checkerboard' sneaker is a playful expression of the 1976 skate icon. Debuted in February 2018, this kids' edition features the cartoon character's face throughout the canvas upper and on the tongue tag. Signature elements return via the heel zipper, sidestripe and textured midsole. Continuing the theme, a splattered Plankton is screen-printed on the Waffle outsole.

results.name: Authentic LX Toddler 'Spongebob'
results.story: Part of the February 2018 limited edition collaboration between Vans and SpongeBob SquarePants, the toddlers’ edition of the OG Authentic LX ‘Spongebob’ features a playful take on Vans’ signature checkerboard pattern. The pattern is showcased on the canvas side panels, while each white square features SpongeBob’s likeness. The vamp is constructed from Off-White suede, alongside additional hits of Off-White on the eyelets, midsole and laces. Underfoot, the waffle outsole is adorned with a squashed Plankton graphic.

results.name: Authentic LX Toddler 'Spongebob'
results.story: Released in February 2018 as part of a larger collaboration between Vans and SpongeBob SquarePants, this toddlers’ version of the Authentic LX features a black canvas upper adorned with some of the colorful characters from the animated Nickelodeon show, as well as various pieces of marine fauna. The multi-hued design is complemented by contrasting hits of white on the eyelets, midsole, and laces. Underfoot, the waffle outsole is adorned with a squashed Plankton graphic.

results.name: Sk8-Hi Zip LX TD 'Spongebob'
results.story: This toddlers’ version of the Sk8-Hi Zip LX showcases some of Nickelodeon’s SpongeBob SquarePants colorful cast of characters on the canvas side panels. Off-White suede construction is used on the forefoot and heel, with the latter featuring zipper closure for easy on and off. Contrasting black leather appears on the side stripe, and the rubber midsole is finished in more Off-White. Underfoot, a Plankton graphic can be seen on the waffle outsole.
